text: Henry Barbour (fl. 1384–1391), of Reading, Berkshire, was an English politician. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Reading in November 1384 and 1391. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing Category:Year of death missing Category:English MPs November 1384 Category:English MPs 1391 Category:14th-century English politicians Category:People from Reading, Berkshire
